{"tid":1873161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍色肺炎圈] 邊爐家族 兩武漢肺炎患者為美心 廚師 及 樓面","createTime":"2020-02-10T13:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T13:25:27.000Z","uid":113000,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a48839d4db406ae89d72a18ab6ac9c4d9dee0aba","tid":1873161,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/finance/player?newsId=380096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380096&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4QPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=e2378a9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380096&h=845a267e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/finance/player?newsId=380096</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美心集團旗下北京樓兩名員工確診感染新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n在旺角新世紀廣場的北京樓分店已經拉上大閘，門外貼出通告指，分店一名員工確診新型肺炎，已經在9日晚將全店徹底消毒，即日起暫停營業至23日，所有員工亦需要自我隔離14天。<br />\n<br />\n美心集團聲明指，中環歷山大廈分店另一名員工亦都確診，分店有同樣安排。<br />\n<br />\n兩名員工為親屬關係，其中一人做樓面，出現病徵後已沒有上班，另一人為廚師，現正於醫院接受治療。兩人於1月26日參與觀塘同一家庭的火鍋聚餐，其中部分親友亦確診新型肺炎，公司已主動聯絡衞生防護中心跟進事件。"},{"pid":"18ed2f074fc84ab3cbec971e279c62cfb8ceab09","tid":1873161,"uid":209390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"個天都要收美心皮"},{"pid":"0c3f2ff5fe0c5e136d634fe8067ff26c0ec54c54","tid":1873161,"uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"藍絲返大陸去藍店<br />\n仲要廚師為患者<br />\n大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b028067c0bae1692f2079f5a76ea7cd5247f9526","tid":1873161,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"遊行唔到，集會唔到。至少要Home Office 抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1873140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1873140</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d4a946483a14b7486c8f0bba35eec0859f5b793","tid":1873161,"uid":124439,"like"